<item>
            <title>[LU-761] Return values of ll_prep_md_op_data() should be checked using IS_ERR().</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-761</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Several places test to see if ll_prep_md_op_data() returned NULL.  Others assume all errors are due to out of memory.  Still other&apos;s dont check it at all when they should.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
